Remedent
Remedent Inc. serves consumers and the dental community with unique porcelain veneer, teeth whitening, sensitivity and oral hygiene products that are recognized worldwide for their technological superiority and unique ease-of-application.
 » read more about our company


Our Mission
Remedent aims to become the Worldwide N�1  Dental Service Provider in the direct to consumer market, by use of its state of the art technologies and marketing concepts, of which  the combination creates  a unique "feel good" experience, which takes away people's dental fear factor and grows the overall Dental Business. 






