Sep. 17th 2014
The Opening of GlamSmile Madrid
Last week I attended the opening of the GlamSmile Studio in Madrid. It is our franchise partner, José Avila, his first studio for GlamSmile Iberica. I was really impressed by the look and the feeling the Studio gave me. GlamSmile Spain did an exquisite job in installing their first studio, located in Calle de Goya 102, Madrid. There even was a ‘GlamSmile Scent’ in the Studio.
To launch their Studio GlamSmile Madrid was present at the Madrid Fashion Week. Check out some pictures of the new studio here, a picture of the Madrid Fashion Week you can see here.
I wish our new franchises partner all the luck with their new Studio and may it be the first of many in Portugal and Spain!
