	IDS Cologne was a great success. Remedent had a booth of 70 m² and more than 10 people to represent our different products and concepts. The brand new SmileMe Mirror, an instant smile simulator, was shown for the first time. Huge interest from dental clinics worldwide convince us of the practical use of this new in-office marketing concept. Of course we welcomed the many GlamSmile partners from all over the world. Thanks to you all for your enthousiasm in making GlamSmile a global success.  Last but not least I would like to highlight our partnership with Biotech regarding the River8 prêt-à-porter veneers. Obviously a new success story is born. 
