May. 29th 2012
Wenzhou

	A lot of exciting things happening. Our Chinese studios have posted 2 record months back to back and are on track to do this for the 3 rd month in a row. Our Beijing studio (oldest one) is doing increasinly better. We are signing two more studios in June for opening after the summer. We are currently tracking between 3.3 and 3.5 million rmb on a monthly basis. Our goal is to reach a run rate of 10 million rmb per month in 12 months time. That would put us in a perfect position to start thinking listing in HK for 2014. Our ebitda is still incredible, cash flow positive and 5 million usd investment in the bank. In the early part of May we had the official opening of the Wnzhou store. We got our license the month before.

	On the franchise front. We had a big meeting with our franchisees in April. A lot of excitement there as well. We look forward in the opening of 3 more of our franchises at the end of this quarter.

	 

	This is our year end closing so a little more patience with the release of numbers. 

	 

	 
