			Company Description 
		


                Remedent, Inc. specializes in the research, development, and manufacturing of oral care and cosmetic dentistry products. Its products include veneers, whitening solutions, and consultancy services. The company was founded on September 30, 1996 and is headquartered in Ghent, Belgium.
            




